Effects of creatine supplementation on nutritional status, muscle function and 
quality of life in patients with colorectal cancer--a double blind randomised 
controlled trial.

Norman K(1), Stübler D, Baier P, Schütz T, Ocran K, Holm E, Lochs H, Pirlich M.
